input_str: The Manic Pixie Dream Girl (MPDG) trope has been covered extensively in pop culture, from Elizabethtown to Silver Linings Playbook – man is sad, depressed or troubled, man meets spritely woman who shows him life's little joys and seems to exist for no other purpose, the pair live happily ever after.
